  $(EDK_SOURCE)/Foundation/Cpu/Pentium/Include
  $(EDK_SOURCE)/Foundation/Framework/Guid/DataHubRecords
  $(EDK_SOURCE)/Foundation/Framework/Guid/StatusCodeDataTypeId

